467
00:38:38,720 --> 00:38:41,600
In your post you wrote about how just 
the life of forward deployed engineers  

468
00:38:41,600 --> 00:38:45,040
is pretty crazy. You just get a call 
sometimes like, "Hey, you're flying to  

