00:38:45,040 --> 00:38:50,640
this random country tomorrow. Get ready." Is 
that just life as a forward deployed engineer?

470
00:38:50,640 --> 00:38:54,480
It is. Yeah. The company had a very, I would say,  

471
00:38:54,480 --> 00:38:58,640
aggressive attitude towards travel in the sense 
of when you join, you were basically told, "Look,  

472
00:38:58,640 --> 00:39:02,640
